OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777468272
OL,3,CRoad-roller smashes through public
OL,4,Ctoilets causing #10,000 of damage
OL,6,FA public toilet block in the New
OL,7,FForest has been completely destroyed
OL,8,Fafter a road-roller smashed through
OL,9,Fthe building.
OL,11,FForestry England says more than
OL,12,F#10,000 worth of damage has been
OL,13,Fcaused to the block at the Anderwood
OL,14,Fsite, on Lyndhurst Road in Burley.
OL,16,FThe agency which is responsible for
OL,17,Fmanaging England's public woodlands
OL,18,Fand forests said the damage is so bad
OL,19,Fthat the toilet block will have to be
OL,20,Fdemolished.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
