OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777468272
OL,3,CRoad-roller smashes through public
OL,4,Ctoilets causing #10,000 of damage
OL,6,FA Forestry England spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"This awful damage has been reported
OL,8,Fto the police and is being
OL,9,Finvestigated.
OL,11,F"If anyone has any information about
OL,12,Fthe incident we would encourage them
OL,13,Fto contact the police.
OL,15,F"The toilet block, signs, and
OL,16,Fmachinery being used to repair the car
OL,17,Fpark, were all damaged in the attack.
OL,19,F"The damage to the toilet block is so
OL,20,Fbad that we will have to demolish it.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
