PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777468272
OL,3,CRoad-roller smashes through public
OL,4,Ctoilets causing #10,000 of damage
OL,6,F"Replacing the toilet block and
OL,7,Frepairing all of the damage is likely
OL,8,Fto cost more than #100,000.
OL,10,F"This is money, paid by those who park
OL,11,Fand our members, that should be used
OL,12,Fto look after the forest and improve
OL,13,Ffacilities for those visiting.
OL,15,F"Instead, we will now have to spend it
OL,16,Fon repairing the damage caused by a
OL,17,Fsmall number of individuals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
